      " style="font-size:inherit;line-height:inherit;font-style:normal"><a href="mailto:france-chaleur-urbaine@developpement-durable.gouv.fr">france-chaleur-urbaine@developpement-durable.gouv.fr</a></span></p><ul class="fr-footer__content-list"></ul></div></div><div class="fr-footer__partners"><h4 class="fr-footer__partners-title">Nos partenaires</h4><div class="fr-footer__partners-logos"><div class="fr-footer__partners-main"><a href="http://www.driee.ile-de-france.developpement-durable.gouv.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" title="Lien vers le site du partenaire" class="fr-footer__partners-link fr-raw-link"><img alt="DRIEAT" style="height:5.625rem" src="/logo-DRIEAT-white.png" class="fr-footer__logo"/></a></div><div class="fr-footer__partners-sub"><ul><li><a href="https://www.gouvernement.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" title="Lien vers le site du partenaire" class="fr-footer__partners-link fr-raw-link"><img alt="Gouvernement" src="/logo-government.svg" style="height:5.625rem" class="fr-footer__logo"/></a></li><li><a href="https://www.ademe.fr/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" title="Lien vers le site du partenaire" class="fr-footer__partners-link fr-raw-link"><img alt="ADEME" src="/logo-ADEME.svg" style="height:5.625rem" class="fr-footer__logo"/></a></li></ul></div></div></div><div class="fr-footer__bottom"><ul class="fr-footer__bottom-list"><li class="fr-footer__bottom-item"><a class="fr-footer__bottom-link" href="/accessibilite">Accessibilité : non conforme</a></li><li class="fr-footer__bottom-item"><a class="fr-footer__bottom-link" href="/mentions-legales">Mentions légales</a></li><li class="fr-footer__bottom-item"><a class="fr-footer__bottom-link" href="/politique-de-confidentialite">Données personnelles</a></li><li class="fr-footer__bottom-item"><button id="fr-consent-modal-control-button" aria-controls="fr-consent-modal" data-fr-opened="false" class="fr-footer__bottom-link">Gestion des cookies</button></li><li class="fr-footer__bottom-item"><a cla